$string['moodleparamshelp'] ='<p><strong>Note: Some awareness of the Moodle code is required here! and you can <em>seriously</em> break your server</strong></p><p>This setting allows you to specify Moodle variables that will be passed to the Widget.</p><p>Each item should be separated by a comma and takes the form of <em>widgetPreferenceName</em>=<em>moodleVariable</em>. e.g. <code>courseid=$COURSE->id</code> will pass the Moodle <code>$COURSE->id</code> variable to the widget as <code>courseid</code>.';